org.bus1.rdinit: /init to use in the initrd:
 - mouts /dev, /sys, /proc
 - starts org.bus1.devices
 - reads the kernel commandline:
   - "disk=UUID" searches and finds the disk with the given GPT UUID,
     searches and finds the first GPT partition with the GPT partition
     type UUID of e0243462-d2d0-4c3b-ad28-b365f2da3b4d
   - root=<partition device node> specifies the partition device node
     to mount
 - mounts the bus1 partition to /bus1
 - mounts the system squashfs image in /bus1/system/ to /usr
 - mounts /bus1/data to /var
 - executes org.bus1.init

org.bus1.devices: hotplug device manager and kernel module loader
 - listens to kernel uevents
 - crawls /sys for coldplug
 - adjusts platform permissions in /dev
 - loads kernel modules for plugged devices

org.bus1.init
 - starts org.bus1.devices
 - starts bash
